gemini_raw_text:
{
  "strength": "The image has a strong, painterly atmosphere, using fog and soft light to create a serene and mysterious mood.",
  "weakness": "The composition includes an excessive amount of empty white space in the top half of the frame, which diminishes the visual impact of the trees and rocks below.",
  "verdict": "not selected because the composition feels unbalanced due to the large, empty area of sky/fog at the top, which overpowers the subject."
}

{
  "strength": "The subjects are perfectly in focus and evenly lit, highlighting the vibrant colors and soft textures of the plush toys.",
  "weakness": "The plain, neutral background, while effective for subject isolation, is somewhat sterile and lacks any environmental context.",
  "verdict": "selected because the image is a high-quality product shot with excellent clarity, vibrant colors, and a clean composition that makes the subjects appealing."
}

{
  "strength": "The subject is well-lit with a pleasant, engaging expression, and she is clearly the focal point of the image.",
  "weakness": "The background is distracting, split between a dark wood-paneled wall and a light-colored textured wall, which pulls attention from the subject.",
  "verdict": "not selected because the distracting, split background and flat lighting are characteristic of a standard event photograph rather than a high-quality portrait."
}

{
  "strength": "The high-contrast black and white processing creates a dramatic and visually striking image, emphasizing the intricate textures of the iris and eyelashes.",
  "weakness": "The highlights on the sclera, particularly on the left side of the frame, are very bright and verge on being blown out, which slightly detracts from the overall balance.",
  "verdict": "selected because the extreme close-up composition, combined with sharp focus on the iris, creates a powerful and intimate image that is rich in detail and texture."
}

{
  "strength": "The composition is dynamic, with the uncoiled roll of stamps creating interesting curves and a sense of movement against a clean background.",
  "weakness": "The lighting is very soft and even, which results in a lack of strong contrast and shadows, making the image feel somewhat flat and lacking in dimension.",
  "verdict": "not selected because the flat, diffused lighting fails to create enough contrast to give the subject a strong sense of depth and visual pop."
}
